            "type": "text",
            "text": "The LTX-2 19B Distilled FP8 model represents a significant advancement in efficient large language models, combining distillation techniques with FP8 quantization to optimize performance for API-driven applications. This post examines the LTX-2 19B Distilled FP8 benchmark outcomes and offers actionable advice for API teams aiming to leverage its capabilities in production."
